					</div>
									<div id="vers165958" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">8</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Imprisoned, brought to judgement, and carried off, he, whose birth is beyond our knowing; numbered among the living no more! Be sure it is for my peopleâ€™s guilt I have smitten him.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="1532">âœ»</a></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers165959" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">9</div>
